Class GraphPanel

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Component
      java.awt.Container
          javax.swing.JComponent
              javax.swing.JPanel
                  com.isti.traceview.gui.GraphPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Printable, Serializable, EventListener, Observer, Accessible, MouseInputListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
XYZGraphPanel
public class GraphPanel
extends JPanel
implements Printable, MouseInputListener, Observer

This is graphics container; it contains a list of Slot(s) (panels) and renders them as a 1-column table; responsible for Slot selecting and ordering selecting time and values ranges, holds information about current representation state.

Author:
Max Kokoulin
